{
  "script_id": "lorenz-attractor",
  "voice": "zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural",
  "voice_key": "xiaoxiao",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "lorenz-attractor",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lorenz-attractor/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 3.09,
      "size": 49392,
      "text": "一九六三年，气象学家洛伦兹在简化对流模型时，写下了三个看似普通的微分方程。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lorenz-attractor",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lorenz-attractor/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.32,
      "size": 37152,
      "text": "他没想到，这组确定的方程，竟画出了一只永不重复的数学蝴蝶。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lorenz-attractor",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lorenz-attractor/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.26,
      "size": 36144,
      "text": "它彻底改变了我们对可预测性的理解，也点燃了混沌理论的火种。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lorenz-attractor",
      "section_id": "equations",
      "line_id": "eq-1",
      "filename": "equations-eq-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lorenz-attractor/xiaoxiao/equations-eq-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.97,
      "size": 31536,
      "text": "系统有三个变量 x、y、z，随时间连续变化。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lorenz-attractor",
      "section_id": "equations",
      "line_id": "eq-2",
      "filename": "equations-eq-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lorenz-attractor/xiaoxiao/equations-eq-2.mp3",
      "duration": 3.39,
      "size": 54288,
      "text": "x 的变化率等于西格玛乘以 y 减 x；y 的变化率等于 x 乘以 罗 减 z，再减去 y。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lorenz-attractor",
      "section_id": "equations",
      "line_id": "eq-3",
      "filename": "equations-eq-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lorenz-attractor/xiaoxiao/equations-eq-3.mp3",
      "duration": 3.47,
      "size": 55584,
      "text": "z 的变化率等于 x 乘 y，再减去 贝塔 乘 z。方程里有乘积项，这正是非线性的来源。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lorenz-attractor",
      "section_id": "attractor",
      "line_id": "attr-1",
      "filename": "attractor-attr-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lorenz-attractor/xiaoxiao/attractor-attr-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.43,
      "size": 38880,
      "text": "在经典参数下，轨迹被吸向一个固定的区域，但永远不与自己相交。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lorenz-attractor",
      "section_id": "attractor",
      "line_id": "attr-2",
      "filename": "attractor-attr-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lorenz-attractor/xiaoxiao/attractor-attr-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.44,
      "size": 39024,
      "text": "它绕着两个中心不停盘旋，忽左忽右地跳跃，形成蝴蝶的两只翅膀。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lorenz-attractor",
      "section_id": "attractor",
      "line_id": "attr-3",
      "filename": "attractor-attr-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lorenz-attractor/xiaoxiao/attractor-attr-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.48,
      "size": 39600,
      "text": "这个既有界又永不重复的集合，叫做奇怪吸引子，它拥有分形维数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lorenz-attractor",
      "section_id": "butterfly",
      "line_id": "bf-1",
      "filename": "butterfly-bf-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lorenz-attractor/xiaoxiao/butterfly-bf-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.23,
      "size": 35712,
      "text": "让两条轨迹从几乎相同的初始点出发，差异小到千万分之一。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lorenz-attractor",
      "section_id": "butterfly",
      "line_id": "bf-2",
      "filename": "butterfly-bf-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lorenz-attractor/xiaoxiao/butterfly-bf-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.48,
      "size": 39600,
      "text": "起初它们几乎重合，可过不了多久，就分道扬镳，走向完全不同的方向。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lorenz-attractor",
      "section_id": "butterfly",
      "line_id": "bf-3",
      "filename": "butterfly-bf-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lorenz-attractor/xiaoxiao/butterfly-bf-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.8,
      "size": 28800,
      "text": "这就是对初值的敏感依赖，也就是著名的蝴蝶效应。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lorenz-attractor",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lorenz-attractor/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.34,
      "size": 37440,
      "text": "调节参数 罗，看系统如何从螺旋收敛的稳定态，跨入混沌。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lorenz-attractor",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lorenz-attractor/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.83,
      "size": 45216,
      "text": "罗 太小，轨迹会静静地落到一个点；调到二十八附近，蝴蝶才真正展翅。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lorenz-attractor",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lorenz-attractor/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.29,
      "size": 36720,
      "text": "洛伦兹吸引子告诉我们，确定的规则也能孕育出不可预测的行为。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lorenz-attractor",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lorenz-attractor/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.13,
      "size": 34128,
      "text": "有界、非周期、对初值敏感，这三点共同定义了混沌。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lorenz-attractor",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lorenz-attractor/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.27,
      "size": 36288,
      "text": "一只蝴蝶扇动翅膀，或许真能改变远方的风暴，我们下次再见。"
    }
  ],
  "total_duration": 42.220000000000006,
